# This directory holds checked-in benchmark outputs.
#
# Contents (auto-generated by benchmarks/run_benchmark.py):
#   benchmark_metrics.csv     - per-class accuracy, precision, recall, F1, latency
#   benchmark_summary.json    - run metadata and overall stats
#   latency_histogram.png     - inference latency distribution plot
#   benchmark.log             - full run log
#
# To regenerate:
#   python benchmarks/run_benchmark.py          # full run
#   python benchmarks/run_benchmark.py --smoke  # CI smoke test
